      "bio": "Sophia is a licensed clinical social worker and clinical supervisor, specializing in family and child therapy. She is EMDR trained and certified in Brainspotting.\n\nHer approach centers on helping families find language for what has gone unspoken, and on meeting children where they already are — in play, in movement, in story.",
